<H2>
Information for Academic Visitors
</H2>

<center><img src="z7626.thm.jpg"></center><p>


<P>Visitors are welcome ...

<P> The University of Oxford offers some support to visitors from the
USA through the <a
href="http://www.admin.ox.ac.uk/prizes/fp/astor.htm">Astor Travel
Fund</a>.

<P>The Leverhulme Trust has a <a
href="http://www.leverhulme.org.uk/visiting_professorships.shtml">
Visiting Professorship scheme </a> to enable distinguished academics
from overseas to spend between three and ten months at a UK university
in order to facilitate collaboration with the host institution and to
enhance the skills of the host researchers and/or teachers.
